The main.css file: 

p.one {
   width: 500px; height: 60px;
    border: 2px solid #c0c0c0;
    margin: 15px; padding: 10px;
}
p.two {
   min-width: 500px; max-height: 60px;
    border: 2px solid #0000ff;
    margin: 15px; padding: 10px; 
}
p.three {
   width: 500px; height: 60px;
    border: 2px solid #ff00ff;
    margin: 15px; padding: 10px;
    line-height: 25px;

}

The main web page with main.css file attached:

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <title>CSS Dimension Application</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="main.css">
    </head
    <body>
        <h3>CSS Dimension Application</h3>
        <p class="one">Hello YouTubers, welcome to software developer channel. Learn programming for free.</p>
        <p class="two">Hello YouTubers, welcome to software developer channel. Learn programming for free.</p>
        <p class="three">Hello YouTubers, welcome to software developer channel. Learn programming for free.</p>
    </body>
</html>
